divs: Sighting DetailsI noticed an unidentified object in the night sky around 11:00 p.m. I was at home and I was outside having a cigarette when I noticed this object. I thought it was very unusual for this object to be bouncing and moving out of orbit. I never lost sight of the object I still see it.
